1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,440
Ji.

2
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:09,120
I used to think you were notorious,

3
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:10,720
and must be a playboy.

4
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:12,320
I never expected

5
00:01:13,240 --> 00:01:14,960
you to be a true gentleman.

6
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:17,560
Young Master.

7
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:18,920
Didn't you say

8
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:21,120
you would help me make a lot of money?

9
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:23,200
How could you leave first?

10
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:25,760
Liu Chuan.

11
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:28,080
I haven't finished writing your story.

12
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:29,610
It shouldn't end like this.

13
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,520
I should have known earlier.

14
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:35,039
You are not him.

15
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,660
Even though Liu Chuan is dead,

16
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:59,180
I will continue to protect everyone for him.

17
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:02,680
Princess.

18
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:04,680
Prince Jia rebelled with ambition

19
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:06,140
and killed so many people.

20
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,860
Are you still so stubborn?

21
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:09,780
Have you forgotten

22
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:11,320
that the young master saved your mother

23
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:12,240
and you?

24
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,160
Just kill me.

25
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,079
I will just accompany Master Liu

26
00:02:16,079 --> 00:02:17,079
and die together.

27
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:20,520
Liu Chuan.

28
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:22,960
I know

29
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,850
you have never liked me.

30
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:27,120
But in my heart,

31
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:30,050
you are still the person I admire the most.

32
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:35,040
I was worried my royal brother would go back on his word

33
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:36,120
and harm you,

34
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:38,360
so I let you go back.

35
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:40,000
You can leave now.

36
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,620
What about you?

37
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,600
I will guard Liu Chuan

38
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,040
on his last journey.

39
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:49,640
Qiuyue.

40
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:51,800
Tell me,

41
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,920
did I beat you this time?

42
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,680
Leave now.

43
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,080
If...

44
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:06,220
if my royal brother suspects him and hunts him down,

45
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:07,720
none of you will escape.

46
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,960
Even if I die,

47
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:18,360
I will avenge you.

48
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:22,880
Qiuyue.

49
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:24,600
You can't.

50
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:25,800
Don't, don't go.

51
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,360
It's dangerous outside.

52
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,440
What time is it?

53
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,920
Time for work.

54
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,400
Where am I?

55
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:37,600
Liu Lang,

56
00:03:37,640 --> 00:03:39,920
I thought I would never see you again.

57
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:41,120
Young Master,

58
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:43,020
Jianqin was worried to death.

59
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,440
I really have to thank

60
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,320
Lord Zhuoran

61
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,120
and Qu Dayou.

62
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,200
I used

63
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:58,780
Lord Zhuoran's medicine.

64
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,450
I also extracted

65
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:02,800
Qu Dayou's antibody serum

66
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,000
for research.

67
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:07,440
As a result, I actually developed an antidote

68
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:08,400
and brewed it.

69
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,280
I made you worry.

70
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,200
Alright.

71
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,520
Alright.

72
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,400
Don't cry.

73
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:27,120
I promise,

74
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:29,120
I will never scare you again.

75
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:32,960
You gave me your word.

76
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:34,360
If you dare lie to me,

77
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,600
I'll beat you up.

78
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:40,360
What should we do now?

79
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:44,200
I almost helped him kill you.

80
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:48,360
Forget it.

81
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,840
It's not your fault.

82
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:54,680
Since he is an enemy to the world,

83
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:56,720
then we

84
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:58,560
will fight him.

85
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:03,920
Your royal brother is coming.

86
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:04,720
I'll hold him off.

87
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,160
Take Brother Liu and leave first.

88
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:06,960
Mother.

89
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,760
If we all leave,

90
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:09,760
what will you do?

91
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:13,640
I failed to guide Prince Jia to be good.

92
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:14,920
I have let down the late Emperor

93
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,520
and my husband, Duke Jia.

94
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:19,250
Now, you are the only ones who can stop him.

95
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:20,800
You must stay alive.

96
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:22,200
Mr. Liu,

97
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:24,050
please take care of Qingyi.

98
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:38,050
Where exactly is Liu Chuan?

99
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,320
Back then,

100
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:42,560
when your mother, my older sister, passed away,

101
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:45,120
the late Emperor ordered you to be adopted by me.

102
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,560
It was because he worried that one day

103
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:48,400
you would make a terrible mistake.

104
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:49,260
Unexpectedly,

105
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:51,040
nothing was changed,

106
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:53,240
wasting all my efforts.

107
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:55,680
Is it wrong for me to take back what is mine?

108
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:56,960
Besides,

109
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:58,520
don't you want to see me

110
00:05:58,520 --> 00:06:00,450
avenge my mother with my own hands?

111
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,640
Everything I do

112
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:04,520
is to better repay you.

113
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,360
You are absolutely insane.

114
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,130
You will never succeed.

115
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,120
Shut up!

116
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:14,360
So,

117
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:17,840
is Liu Chuan dead or not?

118
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:10,720
The whole palace is in chaos now.

119
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:13,320
Prince Jia wants to use the Skull Grass

120
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:14,980
to control the entire palace.

121
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,560
Usurping the throne.

122
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,770
For an operation of this scale,

123
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,960
they must have a backup plan.

124
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,040
Don't tell me

125
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:25,660
they can borrow troops from the King of Hell.

126
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,170
The King of Hell.

127
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:30,980
People in the palace often say

128
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:33,640
that someone wandered into the Palace of Hell just like the Director,

129
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:35,770
and the confessions are all on record.

130
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,720
That means

131
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,320
the Palace of Hell

132
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,720
really exists,

133
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:44,800
and it's right here in the imperial palace.

134
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,880
And that happens to be...

135
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,980
The place where they were drugged

136
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:51,130
is in the palace.

137
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:53,850
But it was only a few days ago

138
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,200
that Prince Jia got the Empress Dowager's permission

139
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:57,200
to freely enter and exit the palace.

140
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,000
What if

141
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,820
there is an inside man?

142
00:08:07,520 --> 00:08:09,520
When you sent me into the palace back then,

143
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:10,480
I knew

144
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:12,760
this day would come sooner or later.

145
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:14,640
Don't forget

146
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:17,100
the position of Empress you promised me.

147
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:33,960
Take care.

148
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,800
Please rest assured, Prince Jia.

149
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:54,360
I

150
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,120
will not fail my mission.

151
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:05,040
Thanks to Prince Jia's guidance and help,

152
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:06,560
I was able to join the new party

153
00:09:06,560 --> 00:09:07,720
and rise rapidly.

154
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,440
Your great kindness,

155
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:11,000
I will never forget.

156
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,800
From now on,

157
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,320
we are one.

158
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,860
When we succeed in the future,

159
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:24,120
we will share the world.

160
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:28,180
Thank you, Prince Jia.

161
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:38,440
Rest assured.

162
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:42,160
Once I ascend the throne,

163
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:44,650
who else but you can be the empress?

164
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:48,520
Now that we have the antidote,

165
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:51,440
they will be my puppets sooner or later.

166
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:54,900
All that's missing is the Empress Dowager's edict.

167
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:58,120
Will she agree so easily?

168
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:02,760
The edict is for the world to see.

169
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,800
As for how I get it,

170
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:08,560
it's none of their business.

171
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:34,400
The Book of Life and Death is just an illusion.

172
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:35,360
Most people

173
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:38,090
were poisoned when they were detained together.

174
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:40,400
And those who were poisoned beforehand

175
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:43,530
were the ones who claimed to have visited Yama's Palace.

176
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:46,920
Gao Lu.

177
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,140
Consort De's maid.

178
00:10:51,520 --> 00:10:52,320
Liu Rong.

179
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,080
North gate guard.

180
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:57,920
Cao San.

181
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:17,130
I have found the Palace of Hell.

182
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:19,240
Where is this place?

183
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:23,260
Consort De's bedchamber.

184
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:26,450
It really is those two adulterers.

185
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:36,280
You can take my life.

186
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:39,760
The state can be yours.

187
00:11:40,160 --> 00:11:42,120
But do not harm His Majesty.

188
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:45,680
Hasn't the Empress Dowager always been dissatisfied

189
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:47,440
with His Majesty's new policies?

190
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:49,600
That's why you made me your pawn.

191
00:11:50,640 --> 00:11:51,200
What?

192
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,530
Are you not happy that His Majesty is dead?

193
00:11:54,920 --> 00:11:56,000
He and I

194
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,780
may have different ideas.

195
00:11:58,400 --> 00:12:00,400
But we both do it for the state.

196
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:01,440
Besides,

197
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,370
he is my own flesh and blood,

198
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:05,120
and I am his mother.

199
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:06,520
Mother.

200
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:08,780
Where is my mother?

201
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,880
Rest in peace, sister.

202
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:14,080
I

203
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:16,200
will definitely make your child

204
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:17,760
the Crown Prince.

205
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:36,800
The Third Prince was disrespectful in the presence of the Emperor,

206
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:39,160
and expressed dissatisfaction with the new Empress

207
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:40,680
through rebellious words.

208
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:43,010
He is hereby stripped of his royal status,

209
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:45,480
and adopted into the Duke of Jia's household.

210
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:46,920
End of decree.

211
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:18,920
We must hurry.

212
00:13:53,760 --> 00:13:55,120
I didn't expect King Jia

213
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:56,840
was also a prince before.

214
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:59,520
Later, the Empress Dowager adopted him

215
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:01,180
into the Duke of Jia's family.

216
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:04,320
That's why he covets the throne.

217
00:14:04,640 --> 00:14:05,160
So

218
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:07,520
so many lives have to be sacrificed.

219
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:40,370
Found it.

220
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:43,580
A hidden space and the outer space

221
00:14:43,640 --> 00:14:45,440
will create a pressure difference.

222
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:46,300
I didn't expect

223
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:48,000
the path to Yanluo Palace

224
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:49,000
to be in the cabinet.
